      "text": [
        "4622 - وَ قَالَ عَلِيٌّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"كُلُّ اِمْرِئٍ تُدَبِّرُهُ اِمْرَأَةٌ فَهُوَ مَلْعُونٌ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4622 - Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said: \"Any man who is ruled by a woman is cursed.\""
        ]
      }
    }
